Name: Verify cable type, size, colour code and tags are in accordance with the Cable Schedule.
Check cable cores correctly identified and labelled.
Cable has been installed as per client specification

Testing for the below should be done at 5kV for 10 minutes. If result is below 1.25GΩ this indicates a low test and will need to be re tested. A brand new cable should have a result above 2GΩ. Please insert photo of test results.
